le / android pay 可以 check 返每一單 transaction record<br />\n買平野又得 買貴野又得</blockquote><br />\n個人層面：做唔到P2P<br />\n商戶層面：除交易費外仲要整部機，唔係間間都夠單做呢樣嘢，收費最後只會轉嫁到消費者身上</blockquote><br />\n呢兩樣嘢其實好似殊途同歸<br />\n只要有P2P<br />\n商戶用八達通應該會更方便<br />\n成本應該都會降低</blockquote><br />\n有P2P之後個收費模式肯定會有改變<br />\n我都好希望有多啲P2P solutions出到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3c0af58846a771d0174130ff2b6f76f8bf8b7b","tid":300114,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"已經有啦"},{"pid":"c9ba34dc6d4c62485574a81eb59380424accb406","tid":300114,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\napple / android pay 可以 check 返每一單 transaction record<br />\n買平野又得 買貴野又得</blockquote><br />\n個人層面：做唔到P2P<br />\n商戶層面：除交易費外仲要整部機，唔係間間都夠單做呢樣嘢，收費最後只會轉嫁到消費者身上</blockquote><br />\n商戶用八達通收錢一樣要畀交易費同租機架</blockquote><br />\n暫時商戶真係樣樣都要俾錢嘅，都好正常。<br />\n商戶層面嗰個只係講到Apple pay嘅不足，講唔到同八達通嘅比較。<br />\n<br />\n八達通而家個oepay好似會做到P2P，我仲等緊account upgrade去試"},{"pid":"f8fac41eee545b98c08f74c3508225281443e968","tid":300114,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"八達通個P2P好處係可以直接由八達通轉錢落o2pay, 唔需要捆綁銀行咭<br />\n<br />\n不過iPhone冇內置NFC，操作起黎麻煩好多"},{"pid":"a2af9e4367f196cc51a8ad8491e64ad973227f14","tid":300114,"uid":10703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>匯豐payme</blockquote><br />\n呢個真心好，但好少人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n積極介紹比friend用，出街食飯唔帶錢都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎黎去去都係得個幾個對technology 比較sensative既friend用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8